        "Description": "47!!! YOU HAVE AN F IN YOUR MATHEMATICS CLASS AT THE ICA!!! Wait, why do I care? I just tell you what to do. Well, anyway, let&apos;s try and start off with some easier equations to raise that grade up, shall we? How about this:\r\rAntique Knives + Pistols + Explosions = Antique Explosive Pistols\r\rPretty simple huh? Let&apos;s hope. Good luck.\r\rYour Mom Friend, Diana Burnwood",
